title: Your Pre-Draft Cheat Sheet for Your Cheat Sheet | The Dantasy Football Podcast (Ep. 291)
description:
The Ringer’s Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly list their “thank me later” players to target in drafts (01:30) and break down the players with the biggest gaps in ESPN and Yahoo ranks (14:00). Then the Dannies discuss players popular with sharp drafters this year (27:45)
